        "TileImage": "$($repository d4afe9b1-8e6d-4e2d-83a7-58b78312ccbd).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning, 47.\r\rYour location for this contract is the touristic paradise of Sapienza. Your first target is Claudia Di Meo, the previous Sous Chef to world renowned Chef Marcello Ray, has recently been fired due to carelessness and accidentally cooking a sauce with expired ingredients. She has vowed revenge on Marcello during her last day of work, and he now fears for his life.\r\rYou will also need to kill her boyfriend, Claudio Spaghetti. Marcello believes they are in cahoots.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
